        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-pill">
        <div class="service-pill__icon">🔬</div>
        <div class="service-pill__text">
          <strong>Hongos en uñas</strong>
          <span>Diagnóstico y tratamiento antifúngico</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-pill">
        <div class="service-pill__icon">💉</div>
        <div class="service-pill__text">
          <strong>Pie diabético</strong>
          <span>Cuidado especializado y preventivo</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-pill">
        <div class="service-pill__icon">🩺</div>
        <div class="service-pill__text">
          <strong>Callos y durezas</strong>
          <span>Extracción y tratamiento de fondo</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-pill">
        <div class="service-pill__icon">🏠</div>
        <div class="service-pill__text">
          <strong>Podología a domicilio</strong>
          <span>En tu casa, por toda Medellín</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-pill">
        <div class="service-pill__icon">⚡</div>
        <div class="service-pill__text">
          <strong>Verruga plantar</strong>
          <span>Tratamiento con técnica especializada</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-pill">
